111
00:06:06,700 --> 00:06:07,020
Song.

112
00:06:39,260 --> 00:06:39,780
Ms. Song.

113
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:41,020
Ms. Song.

114
00:06:42,540 --> 00:06:44,700
