131
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:48,740
Whether I like the painting or not?

132
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:50,060
That's right.

133
00:08:03,740 --> 00:08:05,220
I think no one has asked me

134
00:08:05,300 --> 00:08:06,140
