168
00:10:21,980 --> 00:10:22,420
Nice to meet you.

169
00:10:22,420 --> 00:10:24,220
This is Song Yao, my wife.

170
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:07,100
Please.

171
00:11:07,940 --> 00:11:08,500
Let's go.

172
00:11:32,580 --> 00:11:33,980
